Package cryptoTrader.utils

Class TradeResult

java.lang.Object
cryptoTrader.utils.TradeResult
public class TradeResult
extends java.lang.Object
Class that stores the result from the trades. Includes information for all columns in trade log table Each trade made creates a separate TradeResult object
Author:
Ali Mohamed, Ian Guenther Green
